{"tid":1539190,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「民陣入」五大訴求，缺一不可！","createTime":"2019-09-04T09:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T11:32:36.000Z","uid":78392,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3feaeb53b1e2ddffe0402076ec4e682f3aa1886c","tid":1539190,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:10:32.000Z","msg":"先唔講今晚可能係宣佈戒嚴 or 緊急法<br />\n如果只係撤回惡法<br />\n<br />\n民陣準備再搞多次2百萬人大遊行！"},{"pid":"3f3d1d701d37f252d2696c8a579578b501604634","tid":1539190,"uid":295304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:11:16.000Z","msg":"有冇見過兇殺案由政府新聞處公佈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535010</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇埋回覆先留言，因為分析我放咗喺回覆<br />\n<br />\n成個熱門勁多都係講林鄭撤回嘅風，<br />\n但而家佢撤唔撤回都好，831太子站有冇死人、有冇極嚴重傷勢受害人，呢d都係要查啊！唔好俾佢轉移焦點啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好認真，點解一路發生咁多件事，都冇話撤回，突然今日會講起？到底呢幾日發生咗咩事逼到佢要做野？係咪真係其實死咗人？就算冇死人，到底情況係幾嚴重？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要求黨鐵交出831太子站完整CCTV記錄啊！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"7bf542487ffdf45406c242d2fac4cb596d3222da","tid":1539190,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:11:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a62abfa9e1dcd23005d19be0eb15be9eadca3c79","tid":1539190,"uid":198175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:12:48.000Z","msg":"今日先有人爆料大陸落咗幾隻貨櫃的軍事物資嚟咗香港老解基地, 你估裡面全部都係被呢?<br />\n<br />\n近幾日仲玩緊嘅篤灰白色恐怖, 方向報今日仲吹緊急法, 克驚無限制濫暴都冇停過.<br />\n<br />\n口頭話撤回, 遲吓再搞個真相調查委員會嚟魚目混珠, 零成本玩分化<br />\n<br />\n搞咁多嘢, 一手硬一手軟, 玩分化拉一派打一派, 根本就係用嚟buy time拖時間, 降低反抗熱度同意志, 盡量要美國國會用低票通過香港人權民主法案, 只要唔夠2/3通過, 就呃侵侵同意trade deal去換取否決香港人權民主法案, 之後再收搭你班港毒分子大清算玩新疆模式, 捉晒D廢青去再教育, 然後順便走埋侵侵trade deal條數, 過咗海就係神仙.<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求, 缺一不可!"},{"pid":"2ee37973c83e0fab13424dad8bf79ec74c6faccc","tid":1539190,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPZtn7J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPZtn7J.jpg&h=e8723917&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/04/131440_50b7dede60f035f83368a40ef105bb64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F04%2F131440_50b7dede60f035f83368a40ef105bb64.png&h=cd298bf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iWZ88C6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiWZ88C6.jpg&h=98b04a58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"237c6844fde5e4fc82a7ffb4409c68e7a52cfc83","tid":1539190,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:13:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">六大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iHJFfmd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiHJFfmd.jpg&h=5166b6cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8dad53b9b0d4b28c19741447aa196acbfe9b3129","tid":1539190,"uid":279085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T0EhhKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn